Product Version     25.10    Cadence Design Systems, Inc.
ui_view_box(25.10)                                          ui_view_box(25.10)

Name
       ui_view_box  - Reports the coordinates of the current area being viewed
       in the GUI

Syntax
       ui_view_box [-help]

       Reports the coordinates of the current area being viewed in the GUI.

Parameters
       -help  Prints out the command usage. For a detailed description of  the
              command, use the man command:

              man ui_view_box

Example
       The following command reports the coordinates of the current area being
       viewed in the GUI:

       innovus 9> ui_view_box

       93.367 -646.465 103.294 -638.724

Related Information
              * zoomBox

